keyToStrMap.Full:
Dorothy the Doctor

Occupation:
[] Doctor (previously professional jockey)

Likes:
[] Horse riding, shooting, swimming in the sea

Dislikes:
[] Lazy people, getting up late

Favourite quote:
[] An apple a day keeps the doctor away

Favourite people in the (living) world:
[] My horse Black Jack

How I came to be here:
[] Thrown off an unruly horse

What I wish:
[] To be able to ride Black Jack along the beach again
